\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Treatment mortality for beetles forced to swim in the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

witch's brew
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is high and continues to rise with each iteration.
 However, control mortality is high, about 30-40%, mainly due to the fungal
 pathogen, 
\emph on
Metarhizium majus
\emph default
.
 We have attempted to filter out fungal spores by passing the brew through
 a serious of filters with the last stage being a Millipore 0.45 micron filter,
 which should block all fungal spores while allowing virus particles to
 pass through.
 Unfortunately, this idea has not worked because filters get totally plugged.
\end_layout

