Mortality of beetles forced to swim in the witch's brew.
 
\series bold
Treatment mortality
\series default
 is corrected for control mortality using Abbott's formula.
 
\series bold
p
\series default
 is the probability of treatment mortality exceeding control mortality by
 chance (Fisher's exact test).
\end_layout

